{"tid":112313,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"大家點睇brexit?","createTime":"2017-02-08T05:09:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T10:35:35.000Z","uid":29994,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"142cc8921ae86c2ed603ce3866e5d5f2ad3f3a7d","tid":112313,"uid":29994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T05:09:49.000Z","msg":"我個人認為<br />\n<br />\n短期會有影響<br />\n但長期黎講應該會比係歐盟既時候好<br />\n<br />\n但出面啲風係咁話英國會一沉不起<br />\n想知連登仔點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 早輪入左啲pound做long term investment<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117b3867a5323fcf59c34756fa6d9d8b0a8ba4ea","tid":112313,"uid":29994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T05:13:15.000Z","msg":"正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：一定會更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：死硬"},{"pid":"7c924d0be605e5ed51c8a0632575ae81dcdeb5bb","tid":112313,"uid":5368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T05:18:34.000Z","msg":"坦白話你聽真係有好多英國人想brexit <br />\n因為佢地既人工會相應提高<br />\n(冇得係外國引入專才）<br />\n另外自己既民族主義都高 覺得洗乜靠人<br />\n不如睇下brexit 會唔會有其他國家跟風 例如frexit"},{"pid":"4bfa7e7dd8d31f0facaad35ac739c4ee8767f331","tid":112313,"uid":1424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T05:42:31.000Z","msg":"係法律方面黎講，我睇唔明點解一個sovereign state 要俾其他EU Member State 既law 局限住<br />\n仲要佢係EU 入面惟一一個行common law 既國家<br />\n<br />\n另外經濟方面，而家EU 都長貧難顧，而英國都只係可以算岩岩好breakeven<br />\n係唔知幾時會再爆第二個歐豬既時候，俾一筆掟煲費好過唔知幾時又要幫手俾錢<br />\n<br />\n係政治方面，當EU 大部分國家而家都係睇德國頭既時候<br />\n我睇唔到留同唔留對佢既影響力有太負面既影響<br />\n<br />\n利申︰9UP"},{"pid":"caf6f55c749ab9037fac8095100861d3c2db623e","tid":112313,"uid":29994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T08:27:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>坦白話你聽真係有好多英國人想brexit <br />\n因為佢地既人工會相應提高<br />\n(冇得係外國引入專才）<br />\n另外自己既民族主義都高 覺得洗乜靠人<br />\n不如睇下brexit 會唔會有其他國家跟風 例如frexit</blockquote><br />\n岩岩睇新聞 <br />\nLe Pen話會推frexit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bba47793bed55ada9d7c5192f954cbcaa270a8d","tid":112313,"uid":29994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T08:29:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係法律方面黎講，我睇唔明點解一個sovereign state 要俾其他EU Member State 既law 局限住<br />\n仲要佢係EU 入面惟一一個行common law 既國家<br />\n<br />\n另外經濟方面，而家EU 都長貧難顧，而英國都只係可以算岩岩好breakeven<br />\n係唔知幾時會再爆第二個歐豬既時候，俾一筆掟煲費好過唔知幾時又要幫手俾錢<br />\n<br />\n係政治方面，當EU 大部分國家而家都係睇德國頭既時候<br />\n我睇唔到留同唔留對佢既影響力有太負面既影響<br />\n<br />\n利申︰9UP</blockquote><br />\nAgger<br />\n望緊EU逃亡潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a49bbf1d6e4eae1d8cf70ddcd7a50f5717e24bc","tid":112313,"uid":49260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T11:02:21.000Z","msg":"英國正式做美國隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bf977d7c260639fb02d0d3c62b066a3024925e2","tid":112313,"uid":37063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T11:09:29.000Z","msg":"風吹出黎係比放風出黎既人賺錢<br />\n<br />\n如果渣住英磅 怕既未去英國買樓 無對換無損失<br />\n我無持有英磅 但我想佢穿9$<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能風吹到3月時 又話軟脫歐 又加上弱磅令英國 經濟數據強勁 達成一系列歐國協議<br />\n一下反彈上10$"},{"pid":"c5141a69df21f8288bc721b3e51015dcb1076e52","tid":112313,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T12:16:29.000Z","msg":"Frexit <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6216bc4f9993b900e9db9deeb7cd2f2dec72db15","tid":112313,"uid":46254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T13:02:14.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"5b70d9cfac2c75240b369e4363b1d69df56bb4c7","tid":112313,"uid":29994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T09:04:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2017-02-09/